{"word":"upozoravati","level":"B1","de":"warnen","en":"to warn","ru":"предупреждать","fr":"avertir","tr":"uyarmak","es_ar":"advertir","examples":[{"hr":"Znakovi upozoravaju vozače na opasnost.","de":"Die Schilder warnen die Fahrer vor der Gefahr.","en":"The signs warn drivers of the danger.","ru":"Знаки предупреждают водителей об опасности.","fr":"Les panneaux avertissent les conducteurs du danger.","tr":"Levhalar sürücüleri tehlikeye karşı uyarır.","es_ar":"Los carteles advierten a los conductores del peligro."}],"topics":["language-words"]},
{"word":"predviđati","level":"B1","de":"vorhersagen","en":"to predict","ru":"предсказывать","fr":"prévoir","tr":"tahmin etmek","es_ar":"predecir","examples":[{"hr":"Meteorolozi predviđaju toplo vrijeme za vikend.","de":"Die Meteorologen sagen warmes Wetter fürs Wochenende vorher.","en":"Meteorologists predict warm weather for the weekend.","ru":"Метеорологи предсказывают тёплую погоду на выходные.","fr":"Les météorologues prévoient un temps chaud pour le week-end.","tr":"Meteorologlar hafta sonu için sıcak hava tahmin ediyor.","es_ar":"Los meteorólogos predicen tiempo cálido para el fin de semana."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"razvijati","level":"B1","de":"entwickeln","en":"to develop","ru":"развивать","fr":"développer","tr":"geliştirmek","es_ar":"desarrollar","examples":[{"hr":"Tvrtka počinje razvijati novu aplikaciju za učenje jezika.","de":"Die Firma beginnt, eine neue App zum Sprachenlernen zu entwickeln.","en":"The company is starting to develop a new language-learning app.","ru":"Компания начинает развивать новое приложение для изучения языков.","fr":"L'entreprise commence à développer une nouvelle application d'apprentissage des langues.","tr":"Şirket, dil öğrenmek için yeni bir uygulama geliştirmeye başlıyor.","es_ar":"La empresa empieza a desarrollar una nueva aplicación para aprender idiomas."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"unaprijediti","level":"B1","de":"verbessern","en":"to improve","ru":"усовершенствовать","fr":"améliorer","tr":"iyileştirmek","es_ar":"mejorar","examples":[{"hr":"Želimo unaprijediti kvalitetu naših usluga.","de":"Wir wollen die Qualität unserer Dienstleistungen verbessern.","en":"We want to improve the quality of our services.","ru":"Мы хотим усовершенствовать качество наших услуг.","fr":"Nous voulons améliorer la qualité de nos services.","tr":"Hizmetlerimizin kalitesini iyileştirmek istiyoruz.","es_ar":"Queremos mejorar la calidad de nuestros servicios."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"izbjeći","level":"B1","de":"vermeiden","en":"to avoid","ru":"избежать","fr":"éviter","tr":"kaçınmak","es_ar":"evitar","examples":[{"hr":"Da bismo izbjegli gužvu, krenuli smo rano ujutro.","de":"Um den Stau zu vermeiden, sind wir früh am Morgen losgefahren.","en":"To avoid the traffic, we set off early in the morning.","ru":"Чтобы избежать пробок, мы выехали рано утром.","fr":"Pour éviter les embouteillages, nous sommes partis tôt le matin.","tr":"Trafikten kaçınmak için sabah erkenden yola çıktık.","es_ar":"Para evitar el tránsito, salimos temprano por la mañana."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"održavati","level":"B1","de":"instand halten","en":"to maintain","ru":"поддерживать","fr":"entretenir","tr":"sürdürmek","es_ar":"mantener","examples":[{"hr":"Važno je redovito održavati automobil.","de":"Es ist wichtig, das Auto regelmäßig instand zu halten.","en":"It is important to maintain the car regularly.","ru":"Важно регулярно поддерживать автомобиль в исправности.","fr":"Il est important d'entretenir la voiture régulièrement.","tr":"Arabayı düzenli olarak bakımda tutmak önemlidir.","es_ar":"Es importante mantener el auto con regularidad."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"nadomjestiti","level":"B1","de":"ersetzen","en":"to compensate for","ru":"восполнить","fr":"compenser","tr":"telafi etmek","es_ar":"compensar","examples":[{"hr":"Ništa ne može nadomjestiti izgubljeno vrijeme.","de":"Nichts kann die verlorene Zeit ersetzen.","en":"Nothing can compensate for the lost time.","ru":"Ничто не может восполнить потерянное время.","fr":"Rien ne peut compenser le temps perdu.","tr":"Hiçbir şey kaybedilen zamanı telafi edemez.","es_ar":"Nada puede compensar el tiempo perdido."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"olakšati","level":"B1","de":"erleichtern","en":"to facilitate","ru":"облегчить","fr":"faciliter","tr":"kolaylaştırmak","es_ar":"facilitar","examples":[{"hr":"Nova aplikacija olakšava kupnju karata.","de":"Die neue App erleichtert den Kauf von Tickets.","en":"The new app facilitates buying tickets.","ru":"Новое приложение облегчает покупку билетов.","fr":"La nouvelle application facilite l'achat de billets.","tr":"Yeni uygulama bilet almayı kolaylaştırıyor.","es_ar":"La nueva aplicación facilita la compra de entradas."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"otežati","level":"B1","de":"erschweren","en":"to make harder","ru":"затруднить","fr":"rendre difficile","tr":"zorlaştırmak","es_ar":"dificultar","examples":[{"hr":"Loše vrijeme može otežati putovanje.","de":"Schlechtes Wetter kann die Reise erschweren.","en":"Bad weather can make the journey harder.","ru":"Плохая погода может затруднить путешествие.","fr":"Le mauvais temps peut rendre le voyage difficile.","tr":"Kötü hava yolculuğu zorlaştırabilir.","es_ar":"El mal tiempo puede dificultar el viaje."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"uspjeti","level":"B1","de":"gelingen","en":"to succeed","ru":"суметь","fr":"réussir","tr":"başarmak","es_ar":"lograr","examples":[{"hr":"Nadam se da ćeš uspjeti položiti ispit.","de":"Ich hoffe, es wird dir gelingen, die Prüfung zu bestehen.","en":"I hope you will succeed in passing the exam.","ru":"Надеюсь, тебе удастся сдать экзамен.","fr":"J'espère que tu réussiras à passer l'examen.","tr":"Umarım sınavı geçmeyi başarırsın.","es_ar":"Espero que logres aprobar el examen."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"pljusak","level":"B1","de":"der Platzregen","en":"downpour","ru":"ливень","fr":"l'averse","tr":"sağanak","es_ar":"el chaparrón","examples":[{"hr":"Iznenadni pljusak nas je uhvatio bez kišobrana.","de":"Der plötzliche Platzregen hat uns ohne Regenschirm erwischt.","en":"The sudden downpour caught us without an umbrella.","ru":"Внезапный ливень застал нас без зонта.","fr":"L'averse soudaine nous a surpris sans parapluie.","tr":"Ani sağanak bizi şemsiyesiz yakaladı.","es_ar":"El chaparrón repentino nos agarró sin paraguas."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"tuča","level":"B1","de":"der Hagel","en":"hail","ru":"град","fr":"la grêle","tr":"dolu","es_ar":"el granizo","examples":[{"hr":"Tuča je uništila cijeli usjev kukuruza.","de":"Der Hagel hat die gesamte Maisernte vernichtet.","en":"The hail destroyed the entire corn crop.","ru":"Град уничтожил весь урожай кукурузы.","fr":"La grêle a détruit toute la récolte de maïs.","tr":"Dolu bütün mısır ekinini mahvetti.","es_ar":"El granizo destruyó toda la cosecha de maíz."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"poledica","level":"B1","de":"das Glatteis","en":"black ice","ru":"гололёд","fr":"le verglas","tr":"buzlanma","es_ar":"el hielo en la calzada","examples":[{"hr":"Zbog poledice na cesti vozači voze vrlo oprezno.","de":"Wegen des Glatteises auf der Straße fahren die Fahrer sehr vorsichtig.","en":"Because of the black ice on the road, drivers are driving very carefully.","ru":"Из-за гололёда на дороге водители едут очень осторожно.","fr":"À cause du verglas sur la route, les conducteurs roulent très prudemment.","tr":"Yoldaki buzlanma yüzünden sürücüler çok dikkatli gidiyor.","es_ar":"Por el hielo en la calzada, los conductores manejan con mucho cuidado."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"rosa","level":"B1","de":"der Tau","en":"dew","ru":"роса","fr":"la rosée","tr":"çiy","es_ar":"el rocío","examples":[{"hr":"Ujutro je trava bila mokra od rose.","de":"Am Morgen war das Gras nass vom Tau.","en":"In the morning the grass was wet with dew.","ru":"Утром трава была мокрой от росы.","fr":"Le matin, l'herbe était mouillée de rosée.","tr":"Sabah çimenler çiyden ıslaktı.","es_ar":"A la mañana el pasto estaba mojado de rocío."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"inje","level":"B1","de":"der Raureif","en":"hoarfrost","ru":"иней","fr":"le givre","tr":"kırağı","es_ar":"la escarcha","examples":[{"hr":"Grane drveća bile su prekrivene bijelim injem.","de":"Die Äste der Bäume waren mit weißem Raureif bedeckt.","en":"The branches of the trees were covered with white hoarfrost.","ru":"Ветви деревьев были покрыты белым инеем.","fr":"Les branches des arbres étaient couvertes de givre blanc.","tr":"Ağaçların dalları beyaz kırağıyla kaplıydı.","es_ar":"Las ramas de los árboles estaban cubiertas de escarcha blanca."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"grom","level":"B1","de":"der Donner","en":"thunder","ru":"гром","fr":"le tonnerre","tr":"gök gürültüsü","es_ar":"el trueno","examples":[{"hr":"Nakon munje začuo se snažan grom.","de":"Nach dem Blitz war ein lauter Donner zu hören.","en":"After the lightning, a loud thunder was heard.","ru":"После молнии раздался сильный гром.","fr":"Après l'éclair, un puissant tonnerre s'est fait entendre.","tr":"Şimşekten sonra güçlü bir gök gürültüsü duyuldu.","es_ar":"Después del relámpago se escuchó un trueno fuerte."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"mećava","level":"B1","de":"der Schneesturm","en":"blizzard","ru":"метель","fr":"la tempête de neige","tr":"tipi","es_ar":"la tormenta de nieve","examples":[{"hr":"Zbog jake mećave zatvorene su planinske ceste.","de":"Wegen des starken Schneesturms wurden die Bergstraßen gesperrt.","en":"Because of the heavy blizzard, the mountain roads were closed.","ru":"Из-за сильной метели горные дороги были закрыты.","fr":"À cause de la forte tempête de neige, les routes de montagne ont été fermées.","tr":"Şiddetli tipi yüzünden dağ yolları kapatıldı.","es_ar":"Por la fuerte tormenta de nieve, los caminos de montaña fueron cerrados."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"vihor","level":"B1","de":"der Wirbelwind","en":"whirlwind","ru":"вихрь","fr":"la bourrasque","tr":"kasırga","es_ar":"el torbellino","examples":[{"hr":"Vihor je podigao prašinu i lišće s ceste.","de":"Der Wirbelwind wirbelte Staub und Laub von der Straße auf.","en":"The whirlwind lifted dust and leaves off the road.","ru":"Вихрь поднял пыль и листья с дороги.","fr":"La bourrasque a soulevé la poussière et les feuilles de la route.","tr":"Kasırga yoldan toz ve yaprakları havaya kaldırdı.","es_ar":"El torbellino levantó polvo y hojas del camino."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"promaja","level":"B1","de":"der Durchzug","en":"draught","ru":"сквозняк","fr":"le courant d'air","tr":"hava akımı","es_ar":"la corriente de aire","examples":[{"hr":"Zatvori prozor jer je promaja u sobi.","de":"Mach das Fenster zu, denn es zieht im Zimmer.","en":"Close the window because there is a draught in the room.","ru":"Закрой окно, потому что в комнате сквозняк.","fr":"Ferme la fenêtre car il y a un courant d'air dans la pièce.","tr":"Pencereyi kapat, çünkü odada hava akımı var.","es_ar":"Cerrá la ventana porque hay corriente de aire en la habitación."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"sparina","level":"B1","de":"die Schwüle","en":"sultriness","ru":"духота","fr":"la moiteur","tr":"boğucu sıcak","es_ar":"el bochorno","examples":[{"hr":"Ljetna sparina otežavala je disanje u gradu.","de":"Die sommerliche Schwüle erschwerte das Atmen in der Stadt.","en":"The summer sultriness made breathing difficult in the city.","ru":"Летняя духота затрудняла дыхание в городе.","fr":"La moiteur estivale rendait la respiration difficile en ville.","tr":"Yaz boğucu sıcağı şehirde nefes almayı zorlaştırdı.","es_ar":"El bochorno del verano dificultaba la respiración en la ciudad."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"klizište","level":"B1","de":"der Erdrutsch","en":"landslide","ru":"оползень","fr":"le glissement de terrain","tr":"toprak kayması","es_ar":"el deslizamiento de tierra","examples":[{"hr":"Obilne kiše izazvale su klizište na brdskoj cesti.","de":"Heftige Regenfälle haben einen Erdrutsch auf der Bergstraße ausgelöst.","en":"Heavy rains caused a landslide on the hillside road.","ru":"Проливные дожди вызвали оползень на горной дороге.","fr":"De fortes pluies ont provoqué un glissement de terrain sur la route de la colline.","tr":"Şiddetli yağmurlar tepe yolunda toprak kaymasına neden oldu.","es_ar":"Las lluvias intensas provocaron un deslizamiento de tierra en el camino de la ladera."}],"topics":["nature-environment","weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"potres","level":"B1","de":"das Erdbeben","en":"earthquake","ru":"землетрясение","fr":"le tremblement de terre","tr":"deprem","es_ar":"el terremoto","examples":[{"hr":"Jaki potres uzdrmao je cijeli grad usred noći.","de":"Ein starkes Erdbeben erschütterte mitten in der Nacht die ganze Stadt.","en":"A strong earthquake shook the whole city in the middle of the night.","ru":"Сильное землетрясение потрясло весь город посреди ночи.","fr":"Un fort tremblement de terre a secoué toute la ville au milieu de la nuit.","tr":"Güçlü bir deprem gece yarısı bütün şehri sarstı.","es_ar":"Un fuerte terremoto sacudió toda la ciudad en medio de la noche."}],"topics":["nature-environment"]},
{"word":"lavina","level":"B1","de":"die Lawine","en":"avalanche","ru":"лавина","fr":"l'avalanche","tr":"çığ","es_ar":"la avalancha","examples":[{"hr":"Skijaši su na vrijeme pobjegli ispred lavine.","de":"Die Skifahrer sind rechtzeitig vor der Lawine geflohen.","en":"The skiers fled from the avalanche just in time.","ru":"Лыжники вовремя убежали от лавины.","fr":"Les skieurs ont fui l'avalanche juste à temps.","tr":"Kayakçılar çığdan tam zamanında kaçtı.","es_ar":"Los esquiadores escaparon de la avalancha justo a tiempo."}],"topics":["nature-environment","weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"plima","level":"B1","de":"die Flut","en":"high tide","ru":"прилив","fr":"la marée haute","tr":"met","es_ar":"la marea alta","examples":[{"hr":"Za vrijeme plime more je preplavilo obalnu šetnicu.","de":"Während der Flut hat das Meer die Uferpromenade überschwemmt.","en":"During high tide, the sea flooded the coastal promenade.","ru":"Во время прилива море затопило прибрежную набережную.","fr":"Pendant la marée haute, la mer a inondé la promenade côtière.","tr":"Met sırasında deniz sahil yürüyüş yolunu bastı.","es_ar":"Durante la marea alta, el mar inundó la costanera."}],"topics":["nature-environment"]},
{"word":"oseka","level":"B1","de":"die Ebbe","en":"low tide","ru":"отлив","fr":"la marée basse","tr":"cezir","es_ar":"la marea baja","examples":[{"hr":"Za vrijeme oseke djeca su skupljala školjke na pijesku.","de":"Während der Ebbe sammelten die Kinder Muscheln im Sand.","en":"During low tide, the children collected shells on the sand.","ru":"Во время отлива дети собирали ракушки на песке.","fr":"Pendant la marée basse, les enfants ramassaient des coquillages sur le sable.","tr":"Cezir sırasında çocuklar kumda deniz kabuğu topladı.","es_ar":"Durante la marea baja, los chicos juntaban caracoles en la arena."}],"topics":["nature-environment"]},
{"word":"naoblaka","level":"B1","de":"die Bewölkung","en":"cloudiness","ru":"облачность","fr":"la nébulosité","tr":"bulutluluk","es_ar":"la nubosidad","examples":[{"hr":"Do večeri se očekuje povećana naoblaka i kiša.","de":"Bis zum Abend wird zunehmende Bewölkung und Regen erwartet.","en":"Increased cloudiness and rain are expected by evening.","ru":"К вечеру ожидается увеличение облачности и дождь.","fr":"D'ici le soir, on attend une nébulosité accrue et de la pluie.","tr":"Akşama doğru artan bulutluluk ve yağmur bekleniyor.","es_ar":"Para la tarde se espera mayor nubosidad y lluvia."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"vedrina","level":"B1","de":"die Heiterkeit","en":"clear sky","ru":"ясная погода","fr":"le ciel dégagé","tr":"açık hava","es_ar":"el cielo despejado","examples":[{"hr":"Nakon oluje nastupila je potpuna vedrina.","de":"Nach dem Sturm setzte völlig heiteres Wetter ein.","en":"After the storm, a completely clear sky set in.","ru":"После бури наступила совершенно ясная погода.","fr":"Après la tempête, un ciel totalement dégagé s'est installé.","tr":"Fırtınadan sonra tamamen açık bir hava başladı.","es_ar":"Después de la tormenta se instaló un cielo completamente despejado."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"vlažnost","level":"B1","de":"die Luftfeuchtigkeit","en":"humidity","ru":"влажность","fr":"l'humidité","tr":"nem","es_ar":"la humedad","examples":[{"hr":"Ljeti je vlažnost zraka uz more vrlo visoka.","de":"Im Sommer ist die Luftfeuchtigkeit am Meer sehr hoch.","en":"In summer, the air humidity by the sea is very high.","ru":"Летом влажность воздуха у моря очень высокая.","fr":"En été, l'humidité de l'air au bord de la mer est très élevée.","tr":"Yazın deniz kenarında hava nemi çok yüksektir.","es_ar":"En verano, la humedad del aire junto al mar es muy alta."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"oborine","level":"B1","de":"der Niederschlag","en":"precipitation","ru":"осадки","fr":"les précipitations","tr":"yağış","es_ar":"las precipitaciones","examples":[{"hr":"Sutra se očekuju obilne oborine na cijelom području.","de":"Morgen werden im gesamten Gebiet ergiebige Niederschläge erwartet.","en":"Heavy precipitation is expected tomorrow across the whole region.","ru":"Завтра по всей территории ожидаются обильные осадки.","fr":"Demain, de fortes précipitations sont attendues sur toute la région.","tr":"Yarın tüm bölgede yoğun yağış bekleniyor.","es_ar":"Mañana se esperan precipitaciones abundantes en toda la región."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"susnježica","level":"B1","de":"der Schneeregen","en":"sleet","ru":"мокрый снег","fr":"la neige fondue","tr":"sulu kar","es_ar":"el aguanieve","examples":[{"hr":"Cijelo jutro pada hladna susnježica.","de":"Den ganzen Morgen fällt kalter Schneeregen.","en":"Cold sleet has been falling all morning.","ru":"Всё утро идёт холодный мокрый снег.","fr":"Toute la matinée, il tombe une neige fondue glaciale.","tr":"Bütün sabah soğuk sulu kar yağıyor.","es_ar":"Toda la mañana cae un aguanieve frío."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"pahulja","level":"B1","de":"die Schneeflocke","en":"snowflake","ru":"снежинка","fr":"le flocon de neige","tr":"kar tanesi","es_ar":"el copo de nieve","examples":[{"hr":"Prve pahulje polako su padale na tlo.","de":"Die ersten Schneeflocken fielen langsam zu Boden.","en":"The first snowflakes slowly fell to the ground.","ru":"Первые снежинки медленно падали на землю.","fr":"Les premiers flocons de neige tombaient lentement sur le sol.","tr":"İlk kar taneleri yavaşça yere düştü.","es_ar":"Los primeros copos de nieve caían lentamente al suelo."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"mraz","level":"B1","de":"der Frost","en":"frost","ru":"мороз","fr":"le gel","tr":"don","es_ar":"la helada","examples":[{"hr":"Jutarnji mraz oštetio je mlade biljke u vrtu.","de":"Der Morgenfrost hat die jungen Pflanzen im Garten beschädigt.","en":"The morning frost damaged the young plants in the garden.","ru":"Утренний мороз повредил молодые растения в саду.","fr":"Le gel matinal a endommagé les jeunes plantes du jardin.","tr":"Sabah donu bahçedeki genç bitkilere zarar verdi.","es_ar":"La helada de la mañana dañó las plantas jóvenes del jardín."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"bura","level":"B1","de":"die Bora","en":"bora wind","ru":"бора","fr":"la bora","tr":"bora rüzgarı","es_ar":"el viento bora","examples":[{"hr":"Hladna bura zatvorila je most za sav promet.","de":"Die kalte Bora hat die Brücke für den gesamten Verkehr gesperrt.","en":"The cold bora wind closed the bridge to all traffic.","ru":"Холодная бора закрыла мост для всего движения.","fr":"La bora froide a fermé le pont à toute circulation.","tr":"Soğuk bora rüzgarı köprüyü tüm trafiğe kapattı.","es_ar":"El frío viento bora cerró el puente a todo el tránsito."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"jugo","level":"B1","de":"der Schirokko","en":"sirocco","ru":"сирокко","fr":"le sirocco","tr":"lodos","es_ar":"el siroco","examples":[{"hr":"Toplo jugo donijelo je visoke valove na obalu.","de":"Der warme Schirokko brachte hohe Wellen an die Küste.","en":"The warm sirocco brought high waves to the coast.","ru":"Тёплый сирокко принёс высокие волны на побережье.","fr":"Le sirocco chaud a apporté de hautes vagues sur la côte.","tr":"Ilık lodos kıyıya yüksek dalgalar getirdi.","es_ar":"El cálido siroco trajo grandes olas a la costa."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"maestral","level":"B1","de":"der Maestral","en":"maestral wind","ru":"маэстрал","fr":"le mistral","tr":"maestral rüzgarı","es_ar":"el viento maestral","examples":[{"hr":"Ljetni maestral ugodno je rashladio kupače na plaži.","de":"Der sommerliche Maestral hat die Badegäste am Strand angenehm abgekühlt.","en":"The summer maestral wind pleasantly cooled the swimmers on the beach.","ru":"Летний маэстрал приятно охладил купальщиков на пляже.","fr":"Le maestral estival a agréablement rafraîchi les baigneurs sur la plage.","tr":"Yaz maestral rüzgarı plajdaki yüzücüleri hoş bir şekilde serinletti.","es_ar":"El viento maestral del verano refrescó agradablemente a los bañistas en la playa."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"smrzavica","level":"B1","de":"der Eisregen","en":"freezing rain","ru":"ледяной дождь","fr":"la pluie verglaçante","tr":"dondurucu yağmur","es_ar":"la lluvia helada","examples":[{"hr":"Zbog smrzavice svaka je grana bila prekrivena ledom.","de":"Wegen des Eisregens war jeder Ast mit Eis überzogen.","en":"Because of the freezing rain, every branch was covered with ice.","ru":"Из-за ледяного дождя каждая ветка была покрыта льдом.","fr":"À cause de la pluie verglaçante, chaque branche était couverte de glace.","tr":"Dondurucu yağmur yüzünden her dal buzla kaplıydı.","es_ar":"Por la lluvia helada, cada rama quedó cubierta de hielo."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"nevrijeme","level":"B1","de":"das Unwetter","en":"storm","ru":"непогода","fr":"les intempéries","tr":"sağanaklı fırtına","es_ar":"el temporal","examples":[{"hr":"Zbog nevremena otkazani su svi večernji letovi.","de":"Wegen des Unwetters wurden alle Abendflüge gestrichen.","en":"Because of the storm, all evening flights were cancelled.","ru":"Из-за непогоды все вечерние рейсы были отменены.","fr":"À cause des intempéries, tous les vols du soir ont été annulés.","tr":"Sağanaklı fırtına yüzünden tüm akşam uçuşları iptal edildi.","es_ar":"Por el temporal se cancelaron todos los vuelos de la tarde."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"vrućina","level":"B1","de":"die Hitze","en":"heat","ru":"жара","fr":"la chaleur","tr":"sıcak","es_ar":"el calor","examples":[{"hr":"Ljetna vrućina otjerala je sve ljude u hlad.","de":"Die sommerliche Hitze hat alle Menschen in den Schatten getrieben.","en":"The summer heat drove everyone into the shade.","ru":"Летняя жара загнала всех людей в тень.","fr":"La chaleur estivale a poussé tout le monde à l'ombre.","tr":"Yaz sıcağı herkesi gölgeye sürükledi.","es_ar":"El calor del verano hizo que toda la gente buscara la sombra."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"zračni tlak","level":"B1","de":"der Luftdruck","en":"air pressure","ru":"атмосферное давление","fr":"la pression atmosphérique","tr":"hava basıncı","es_ar":"la presión atmosférica","examples":[{"hr":"Nizak zračni tlak često najavljuje promjenu vremena.","de":"Niedriger Luftdruck kündigt oft einen Wetterwechsel an.","en":"Low air pressure often signals a change in the weather.","ru":"Низкое атмосферное давление часто предвещает смену погоды.","fr":"Une basse pression atmosphérique annonce souvent un changement de temps.","tr":"Düşük hava basıncı genellikle hava değişimini haber verir.","es_ar":"La baja presión atmosférica suele anunciar un cambio de tiempo."}],"topics":["weather-seasons","physics"]}
